## 4. Entity Relationship Diagram (ERD)
The schema remains entirely local within the SQLite and ChromaDB instances.

```mermaid
erDiagram
    ORGANIZATIONS ||--o{ GROUPS : "manages"
    ORGANIZATIONS ||--o{ STAFF : "employs"
    GROUPS ||--o{ STUDENTS : "contains"
    GROUPS ||--o{ ATTENDANCE_SESSIONS : "records"
    STUDENTS ||--o{ ATTENDANCE_RECORDS : "marked in"
    ATTENDANCE_SESSIONS ||--o{ ATTENDANCE_RECORDS : "contains"
    
    STUDENTS ||--o| FACE_VECTORS : "local embeddings"
    
    STAFF {
        uuid id PK
        string staff_code UK
        string role "ADMIN/STAFF"
        string hashed_password
    }
    
    ATTENDANCE_SESSIONS {
        uuid id PK
        string status "SCANNING/COMPLETED"
        datetime started_at
    }

    FACE_VECTORS {
        string student_id FK
        vector embedding "512-dim"
    }
```

