## 5. Sequence Diagram: Attendance Workflow
Showing the flow from Browser to Local DB, with the AI-MCP bridge as an optional parallel path.

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Staff / AI Agent
    participant FE as React UI
    participant MCP as MCP Feature (Add-on)
    participant BE as FastAPI Backend
    participant ML as Local Face Engine
    participant DB as SQLite / Chroma

    Note over U, DB: Human-led Path
    U->>FE: Open Scanner
    FE->>BE: POST /recognition/recognize
    BE->>ML: Match Face (CPU)
    ML->>DB: Query Vector
    DB-->>ML: Match Found
    BE->>DB: Save Record (SQLite)
    BE-->>FE: Success

    rect rgba(200, 200, 200, 0.1)
    Note over U, DB: AI-Led Path (Optional Add-on)
    U-)+MCP: Autonomous Prompt
    MCP-)+BE: execute_workflow('take_attendance')
    BE->>DB: Verify State
    BE-->>MCP: Completed
    MCP--)-U: Final Summary Report
    end
```